"""
Ending Soon Deal Engine — v2

Scans eBay for:
  - AUCTION listings ending within 3 hours (snipe targets)
  - BIN (Fixed Price) listings within price range (deal alerts)

Key fixes vs v1:
  - _enrich_with_mv default-arg bug fixed: MAX_MV_COMPUTATIONS now read at call time
  - All 57 players searched (no 12-query cap)
  - Urgent auctions (<30 min) always get MV computed regardless of MAX_MV_COMPUTATIONS
  - BIN search runs in parallel with auction search
  - Full print logging for MV diagnosis
"""

